snippet.title: Hide and Seek - Gamescom Reveal Trailer | Forza Horizon 5
snippet.description:
A new game mode is coming to Forza Horizon 5! Play as the Hider and conceal your presence until you reach your destination, or take the role of one of the Seekers to try and sniff out the Hider, fill your meter and win. Try this new FH5 multiplayer experience coming in September 2024!
